/usr/bin/tex -ini -jobname tex lhplain.ini >/dev/null
/usr/bin/tex -ini -enc -jobname ru lhplain.ini >/dev/null

For MetaPost labels use this:

sed /hoffset/,/catcode...=12/d lhplain.ini >mpost-no-offset.ini
/usr/bin/tex -ini mpost-no-offset.ini >/dev/null
/usr/bin/tex -ini -enc -jobname ru mpost-no-offset.ini >/dev/null

-------------------

\xordcode is used to convert hyphenation tables from koi8-r to cp866 automatically
